{"tid":2264251,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[大學生創業] 四名大學生成功詐騙8百萬","createTime":"2020-10-30T13:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:45:52.000Z","uid":72795,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"79794003005c019a042a4135503bb8f3d5e2f16a","tid":2264251,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"Group project? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA group of students have been arrested in connection with phone scams in which four Hongkongers were conned out of HK$8 million (US$1.03 million) between April and September this year.The four students &ndash; all women aged between 19 and 21 &ndash; were accused of working for con artists who posed as law enforcement officers from mainland China, according to Chief Inspector Mok Tsz-wai of Kowloon East regional crime unit.How Hong Kong phone scammers are trying to cash in on Covid-19 pandemicPolice said&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3107789/four-students-held-conning-many-hongkongers-out-hk8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Flaw-and-crime%2Farticle%2F3107789%2Ffour-students-held-conning-many-hongkongers-out-hk8&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdgNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=2041915c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3107789/four-students-held-conning-many-hongkongers-out-hk8</a>"},{"pid":"c01eb983868a71474f1a0ee18769a7ae852c07d1","tid":2264251,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bd64a0d3a312802e7b65538842fdd394b5ebe8","tid":2264251,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:36:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87fd6fbfc433e